title: p4 main support dearching for 5v5 ranked team
body: Hello, my name is Dominik (ign: civithetank) and im 16 years old im from germany and im searching for an ranked team in plat division my 5v5 ranked team i played in a team wich was gold 1 promo to plat then all left the team im as i said im main support and can play all supports (main thresh) i can play like 4-7 days the week. im searching for an german or international team wich wants to play tournaments and stuff like that. when you are interested in me then contact me ingame or write a comment under the post and i will answer you cya ;)
